_sText:
CT's start at ground level and must engage the terrorists who begin underground.

There are two ladders that descend into the cave, but there is a quicker route for ambitious players who may jump into the underground lake unscathed.

The map may be played very fast depending on the players. I also provided many places for camping and the more strategic playstyles.

I'd play it with up to 24 players, although there are more spawn points.

Happy huntin'
